name: Dr. Kartik Nair
overview:
Dr. Karthik Nair is a trusted and experienced physician specializing in General Medicine, committed to providing comprehensive and patient-centered care. With a focus on accurate diagnosis, preventive medicine, and chronic disease management, Dr. Nair ensures each patient receives tailored treatment based on their individual health needs.

He is known for his compassionate approach, effective communication, and dedication to long-term patient wellness. From routine check-ups to complex internal health issues, Dr. Nair combines evidence-based practices with a deep understanding of general health to support and guide patients through their health journeys.

name: Dr. Maaran. V
overview: "It takes 10 months to bring a life into this world, 4 years to earn a degree, and 5 years to become a doctor. But to become a true leader, it takes a decade of dedication. I believe medicine is not a business  it's a service. Im here to serve, not to sell."
